      "id": "626416633893878",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "HIT now packs a punch!!",
      "review_description": "*Updated Review*\nWOW!! The team at Super Hyper Mega have really put a lot of work into this game recently and it's now so much more than it originally was. It was a basic head smashing sandbox in the beginning but now has so much more to do. \n\nWith objectives to complete to earn cash to unlock more weapons, a wider range of weapons, a oven mini game to bake your favourite heads and display. There's also a car to smash up, or smash heads in to!\n\nOh and you can now smash your favourite creators (including me!) in the face without being arrested!!\nCheck out my new video over on my YouTube!\n😁✌️☮️❤️\n\n*Original Review*\nSuper Hyper Mega are back with their latest game where you can take out your frustrations on clay heads with a variety of weapons. It's currently a little bare bones but I have faith the team will flesh out the game and are always open to feedback and suggestions via their discord.\n\nUltimately it's a fun sandbox that should appeal to all ages.  Check out my first impressions gameplay over on my YouTube channel!\n😁✌️☮️❤️",
      "date": 1747490667,
      "review_helpful_count": 14,
      "author_display_name": "Hippy_Pickle",
